<br>
Another interesting tidbit from a 56 wizard pal of mine. When purchasing potions, there is one potion which, if I recall right, gives you health but later takes it away, like a very small DOT. Supposedly, if you have this potion active, you cannot be hit with a snare/root. Period. Exploit? Maybe. But a lot of people keep that in their arsenals, just in case.<br>
<br>
And forget about killing bards, and at high levels possibly also clerics. Bards are the kings of resists and running and can do some melee besides, and a cleric can very well keep themself healed until you're sick and tired or OOM (one place where melees DO have an advantage, in that you can't out-nuke yourself against a cleric!). But with heavy resists and plenty of no-drop gear, plus preparation, anything is possible. <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#2F2F4F><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub14.ezboard.com/uantaran77.showPublicProfile?language=EN>antaran77</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>knows that Warriors are Superior</span><br>  Posts: 12<br> <font color=#FF0000>(1/14/02 11:23:04 pm)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub14.ezboard.com/fthesteelwarriorthetavern.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=463.topic&index=8>Reply</a>   </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title>   Re: About potions...</span><hr size=1> Golem metal wand in Cazic.....5 charges instant dispell <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#000000><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub14.ezboard.com/uhellra1ser.showPublicProfile?language=EN>HELLRA1SER</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>knows that Warriors are Superior</span><br>  Posts: 19<br> <font color=#FF0000>(1/18/02 2:26:29 am)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub14.ezboard.com/fthesteelwarriorthetavern.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=463.topic&index=9>Reply</a>   <BR><img src=http://hellra1ser.homestead.com/files/SelfPortraits/HELLRA1SER.jpg WIDTH=60 HEIGHT=60></td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title>   Re: About potions...</span><hr size=1> Interesting strategies for PvP servers.  I've never had to use any potions in duels on a blue server.  I've won all as a 60 Warrior except those vs. most monks and bards.  Fights including some vs. a 60 Wizard in GFay, 60 Necro in EC, 60 Pally in SolB, 60 Enc in WFP Arena, and a 60 Mage in SRo.  Basically, you need to play with your prey until they get frustrated and go into aggresive mode.  Then you turn aggresive and beat them down before they think about running.  With pets, deal with them first run them out of range, beat them down to a sliver, run them back and kill them by the caster and beat down the helpless caster.<br>
<br>
A fungi tunic is great for most PvP.  Except vs. Monks.  Monks are just too good.  Very hard to hit and hit very hard.  You need to take advantage of lag and weapon effects vs. them. <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#2F2F4F><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub14.ezboard.com/umintzyfresch.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Mintzy Fresch</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>will KICK YOUR @$$</span><br>  Posts: 427<br> <font color=#FF0000>(1/19/02 1:20:07 am)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub14.ezboard.com/fthesteelwarriorthetavern.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=463.topic&index=10>Reply</a>   <BR><img src=http://members.aol.com/uryvichk/minpro2.jpg width=100 height=145></td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title>   Re: About potions...</span><hr size=1> Well, one thing of note is that PvP servers != duels. Duels can HELP, mind you, but PvP server combat is considerably different. Ambush groups are more common, and you can be attacked in more places than you can imagine, and people can exploit your weakness accordingly (such as, say, casting from the smuggler ledges in HK, rooting you as you pass). Having every possible advantage is very important. And remember that even if you win the FIRST fight... the next guy will see you as an easy mark. <p><CENTER><IMG SRC="http://members.aol.com/uryvichk/mbanner.jpg"></CENTER></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#000000><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub14.ezboard.com/upengieh.showPublicProfile?language=EN>pengieh</A>&nbsp; <IMG SRC="http://www.ezboard.com/ezgfx/gicons/white_fire.gif" BORDER=0></span><br> <span class=usertitle>knows that Warriors are Superior</span><br>  Posts: 4<br> <font color=#FF0000>(1/20/02 8:49:48 am)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub14.ezboard.com/fthesteelwarriorthetavern.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=463.topic&index=11>Reply</a>   </td><td valign=top align=left class